Don Dubbins https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don_Dubbins 0 Donald George Dubbins (June 28, 1928 – August 17, 1991) was an American actor of film and television who in his early career usually played younger military roles, particularly in such classic pictures as From Here to Eternity (1953) and The Caine Mutiny (1954).
